{
  "chapter": 22,
  "chapter_summary": "郭大路和燕七在卫夫人的豪华宅邸中醒来，白衣少女送来酒菜招待。卫夫人现身，承认她一直在试探二人，最终揭示自己是林太平的母亲。林太平逃婚离家，卫夫人担心儿子交友不慎，故设下毒药、大炮等重重考验。见郭大路和燕七不惧死亡、拒绝诱惑，卫夫人放心让他们离去。二人回到小城与王动、林太平团聚，得知活剥皮失踪、利源当铺易主。他们决定不向林太平透露遭遇，让他自由成长。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "我看你睡得正好，不想吵醒你，所以就先来享受了，好在这里的东西多得很，十个人也吃不完。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "是你带我到这里来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "这里是什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "不知道！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你知道什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "我只知道这里的厨子不错，酒也不错，你还等什么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "不吃白不吃，这句话你还没有学会。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "早就学会了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你有没有出去过？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "为什么不出去看看？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "顾得了嘴，就顾不得眼睛了，还是嘴比眼睛重要。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你至少应该先找到这里的主人才是。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "他反正会来找我们的，我们何必急着去找他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_shao_nv",
      "text": "我正愁酒不够，想不到酒已来了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少女",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你既已到了这里，无论想要什么，就有什么。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_shao_nv",
      "text": "我们怎会到这里来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少女",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "当然是这里的主人把你们救来的了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_shao_nv",
      "text": "你就是这里的主人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少女",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你看我像不像？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_shao_nv",
      "text": "不像。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少女",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "我自己看也不像。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_shao_nv",
      "text": "那么这里的主人是谁？我们认不认得他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少女",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "我只知道他一定认得你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_shao_nv",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少女",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "因为，他说你一个人吃的比几个人都多，特地叫我多准备一点酒菜。他若不认得你，怎么会对你如此了解呢？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_shao_nv",
      "text": "这么样看来，他不但认得我，还一定是我的好朋友。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少女",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "请你喝酒的，都是你的好朋友？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_shao_nv",
      "text": "一点也不错。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少女",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "等两位吃饱我就带两位去见这里的主人，他一直都在等着两位。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_shao_nv",
      "text": "我现在已经饱了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少女",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "你怎么一看到我就饱呢？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_shao_nv",
      "text": "因为你长得比一只蹄膀还可爱。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卫夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们又来了么？请进请进。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卫夫人",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你们也不必问我究竟在打什么主意，我的主意本就没有别人能猜得到的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "text": "这句话我相信。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卫夫人",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "还有件事你也不妨相信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卫夫人",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你们现在已可以走了，随时都可以走，无论到哪里去，我都绝不会派人跟踪你们的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "text": "你不想要我们的命了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卫夫人",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "不想。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "text": "你也不想知道林太平的下落了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卫夫人",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "至少目前已不想。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "text": "你费了那么多事来对付我们，现在却随随便便就让我们走了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卫夫人",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "text": "这句话，我实在不能相信。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卫夫人",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "连我的话你都不信？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卫夫人",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你知道我是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "text": "我知道你是个很有钱、很有地位、也很有本事的人，但这种人说的话通常都未必可靠。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卫夫人",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你们一定觉得我做的事很奇怪，但你们若真正知道我是什么人之后，就不会奇怪了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "text": "你究竟是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卫夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我就是林太平的母亲。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "text": "我就相信你真是林太平的母亲，但母亲又怎会不知儿子的下落呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卫夫人",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "这就是做母亲的悲哀，儿子长大了之后，做的事往往就不是母亲所能了解的了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卫夫人",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "这也许只因为他已渐渐变成了个男人。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "text": "他究竟做了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卫夫人",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "他什么也没有做，只不过从家里逃了出去。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "text": "从家里逃了出去？为什么要逃？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卫夫人",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "他逃婚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "text": "逃婚？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卫夫人",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "我看他年纪渐渐大了，就替他订下了门亲事，谁知道他竟在婚礼前的一天晚上，偷偷的逃了出去。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "text": "我明白了，他一定不喜欢那个女孩子。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卫夫人",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "那女孩子他连见都没有见过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "text": "既然没有见过，他怎么知道那女孩子好不好呢？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卫夫人",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "他根本不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "text": "既然不知道好不好，为什么要逃？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卫夫人",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "只因那门亲事是我替他订下来的，所以他就不喜欢。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "text": "老婆是自己的，本就该自己来选才对。你若肯先让他看看那女孩子，他也许就不会逃了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "text": "这并不是说他不孝顺你，但一个男人长大了之后，多多少少总该有一点自己的主意，否则他又怎么能算是男人。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卫夫人",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "我本来也很生气，但后来想了想，反而觉得有点高兴。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "text": "你的确应该高兴，因为像他这么样有主见的男人，世上还不多。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "text": "现在虽然不多，但以后一定会慢慢多起来的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卫夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我现在已改变主意，并不一定要逼他回去成亲了。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卫夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我想一个男孩子在成长的时候，能一个人在外面闯荡闯荡，磨练磨练自己，对他这一生总是有好处的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "text": "这些话你若早点说出来多好。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卫夫人",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "我以前没有说出来，只因为我还有点不放心。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "text": "不放心什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卫夫人",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "不放心他的朋友。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "text": "你那么样做只不过是在试探我们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卫夫人",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你们既然是他的好朋友，想必也不会怪我的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "text": "现在你放心了没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卫夫人",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "现在我已知道，他的朋友非但不惜为他挨饿，为他死，而且还能为他拒绝各种诱惑，在我看来，那比死还困难得多。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卫夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他能交到这种朋友，真是他的运气，我还有什么不放心的。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "六七天不见，你难道也没有一句话问我们？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "问什么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你至少应该问问我们，这几天过得好不好。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "我不必问。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "为什么不必问？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你们只要还能活着回来，就已经很不错了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "可是你至少总应该问问，活剥皮究竟剥谁的皮？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "我也不必问。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "像他那种人，除了剥他自己的皮之外，还能剥谁的皮？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "看样子你们这几天一定玩得很开心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "text": "开心极了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你们知不知道活剥皮已失踪了，利源当铺已换了老板？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "连这种大事都不知道，这两天你们究竟干什么去了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "text": "这两天我们也没干什么，只不过被人毒死过一次，见过一次阎王，又被大炮轰过一次，最后这人请我们大吃大喝了一顿，我们就回来了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "我知道你很会吹牛，但这次却未免吹得太过火了些，只怕连三岁的小孩子都不会相信。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这种事我就知道绝没有人会相信的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 372
    }
